OL,3,CE. coli outbreak: Tesco and Asda face
OL,4,Clegal action after man and girl fall
OL,5,Cill
OL,7,FAn 11-year-old girl at risk of
OL,8,F"permanent kidney damage" and a man
OL,9,Fwho fell ill in the E. coli outbreak
OL,10,Fhas started legal action against
OL,11,Fsupermarkets Tesco and Asda for
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,FLegal firm Fieldfisher, representing a
OL,15,Fgirl from the North West and a man
OL,16,Ffrom the South East, has sent letters
OL,17,Fof claim for violations of the
OL,18,FConsumer Protection Act due to own-
OL,19,Fbrand sandwiches purchased in the
OL,20,Fsupermarkets.
