OL,3,CE. coli outbreak: Tesco and Asda face
OL,4,Clegal action after man and girl fall
OL,5,Cill
OL,7,FThe firm said the claim against Asda
OL,8,Fis related to a girl who has been on
OL,9,Fdialysis for three weeks after
OL,10,Fconsuming an own-brand chicken salad
OL,11,Fsandwich purchased at one of its
OL,12,Fstores and contracting E. coli.
OL,14,F"The girl, aged 11, developed the
OL,15,Fserious condition haemolytic uraemic
OL,16,Fsyndrome (HUS), which attacks the
OL,17,Fkidneys and has been on dialysis for
OL,18,Fthree weeks," it said.
