OL,3,CE. coli outbreak: Tesco and Asda face
OL,4,Clegal action after man and girl fall
OL,5,Cill
OL,7,F"She was discharged home two days ago
OL,8,Fbut could be at risk of permanent
OL,9,Fkidney damage. Her mother bought three
OL,10,Fof the sandwiches as part of an online
OL,11,Fdelivery."
OL,13,FA legal director at the firm,
OL,14,FHarvinder Kaur, said she had issued a
OL,15,Fseparate letter to Tesco on behalf of
OL,16,Fan adult man from the South East who
OL,17,Fwas hospitalised with E. coli symptoms
OL,18,Fafter eating Tesco-branded sandwiches
OL,19,Fcontaining salad.
