OL,5,Cill
OL,7,F"Luckily, this client did not go on to
OL,8,Fdevelop HUS and is now home, but for a
OL,9,Ftime he was seriously ill," she said.
OL,11,F"Under the Act, companies producing
OL,12,Ffood must ensure it is safe to eat. If
OL,13,Fit causes illness, it is a breach of
OL,14,Ftheir duty and those injured are
OL,15,Feligible to claim compensation, not
OL,16,Fleast to fund possible ongoing medical
OL,17,Fcare.
