OL,3,CE. coli outbreak: Tesco and Asda face
OL,4,Clegal action after man and girl fall
OL,5,Cill
OL,7,F"My client was a regular shopper at
OL,8,FTesco, buying his lunch there most
OL,9,Fdays since it was very close to his
OL,10,Fwork."
OL,12,FAn Asda spokesperson told ITV News:
OL,13,F"We have not yet received any letter
OL,14,Ffrom Fieldfisher regarding these
OL,15,Fclaims, as soon as we do we will
OL,16,Freview the details of the claim as a
OL,17,Fmatter of urgency."
OL,19,FITV News understands that Tesco has
OL,20,Falso currently not received a claim
OL,21,Ffrom Fieldfisher.
